  "detailed_description": "<strong>A Walk with Yiayia</strong> is a short adventure game/visual novel about taking your Greek grandmother on a walk around the neighborhood after she's lost her confidence from having a scary fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/4f12aefaf6312cefd8c52dcd7d089803.poster.avif?t=1730491094\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/4f12aefaf6312cefd8c52dcd7d089803.webm?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/4f12aefaf6312cefd8c52dcd7d089803.mp4?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Please wishlist our game! Wishlists are the best way you can support the game before buying it.</strong></h2><br><br><strong>Connect </strong>with Yiayia through engaging conversations, <strong>explore </strong>a <i>beautiful</i>, relaxing environment, and <strong>complete microquests </strong>throughout the neighborhood in this thoughtful, bite-sized adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/b8008d860e04863c990d2b9d2f3ad3f0.poster.avif?t=1730491094\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/b8008d860e04863c990d2b9d2f3ad3f0.webm?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/b8008d860e04863c990d2b9d2f3ad3f0.mp4?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>No fail states, low stress, and an emotional story connecting the experiences between first generation immigrants and their family members, reflecting on what they can learn from each other's experiences. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/8e16e75072fac0bfe7055a80bbd36e5d.poster.avif?t=1730491094\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/8e16e75072fac0bfe7055a80bbd36e5d.webm?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629940/extras/8e16e75072fac0bfe7055a80bbd36e5d.mp4?t=1730491094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A Walk With Yiayia</strong> is an emotional story about inspiring your grandma to get out of her comfort zone and live her life without fear.<br>     <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add A Walk With Yiayia to your Steam Wishlist to get notified when it goes on sale!</h2>",
